name: Trash Tribute
description:
I imagine a future without waste receptacles. Stop the madness!

*Special thanks to ROBNESS V2 for the can.  

*Thank you to long time friend/musician Jeremy Schulz for the drum track.   https://www.beatsfromthecore.com/

Thank you the following artists and collectors for your inspiration: @EmpressTrash @iamwesselart @atMikeyWilson @Henrikaau @andrevv_jones @AprylArt 

Instruments: Conn Baritone saxophone 1921. The saxophone is 101 years old and smells like it! I added Arturia Trash 2 VST to make the sax sound more like a chainsaw. Bass-Zebralette synthesizer, Jeremy Schulz- drums. 

Recorded & Mixed February 2022 - You may use this music for your own project. Right click save. Copy and paste. I don’t care. 

Big love from the green, Marc
